This is a software developed for the Gym enthusiast to track their physical health with their daily calorie count , tracking daily physical exercises , counting daily number of steps of walking , social forum to post the achievements and to make daily streaks to complete some daily alloted task.
It also helps to find for trainers as the trainers can logged in with their details and verified by the admins and after selecting the best suited trainer , one can get the subscription for his/her gym on monthly or yearly basis and trainer can track the daily routines , diets and send weekly feedback with the help of this software.
